---
description: "TDD Lite"
globs: ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx", "**/*.js", "**/*.jsx", "**/*.py"]
alwaysApply: false
---

Use tests-first for regressions and stable public behavior changes: write a failing external-behavior test, confirm it fails, implement the smallest passing change, then refactor if needed. Do not force TDD on trivial edits.
